text: The Unité de formation et de recherche médicale Paris Île-de-France Ouest (in English Paris Île-de-France West Medical Research and Training Departement; also called PIFO or Paris Ouest) is a department of the Université de Versailles Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines focus on research and training activities in medicine. == Further reading == * Official website ==References== Category:Medical education Category:Education in France Category:University of Versailles Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines
